    ns1:competencyCode "CE 10." ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Saber evaluar la seguridad, durabilidad e integridad estructural de los materiales y componentes fabricados con ellos/ Know how to evaluate the safety, durability and structural integrity of the materials and components manufactured with them"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/45000124/2025-26/CE%2011.> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE 11." ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocer los principios econÃ³micos y organizativos de la gestiÃ³n de empresas y saber aplicarlos a la direcciÃ³n de industrias relacionadas con los puntos anteriores/ Know the economic and organizational principles of business management and know how to apply them to the management of industries related to the above points"@es .

